    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚人应将家庭住房货币化以资助退休</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/australians-told-to-monetize-the-family-home-to-fund-retirement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着要求退休人员将投资于房地产的 1.3 万亿澳元（8,700 亿美元）变现的呼声越来越高，过去一年利用政府反向抵押贷款产品来资助退休生活的澳大利亚人数量增加了近 40%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/australians-told-to-monetize-the-family-home-to-fund-retirement</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 21:42:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
